Buenos días Julio.

Tal como se le explicó en la propuesta enviada debe de realizar la actualización del software dado que entre su versión y la actual hay 6 años de diferencia.
En esos 6 años se ha actualizado no solo del software sino también la extrusora que usted precisa adherir el sistema.

Es posible que solo compre la extrusora pero tendrá los productos de hace 6 años atrás por lo que no es recomendado ya que en Alcemar se han incorporado productos, líneas, perfiles y accesorios acordes al desarrollo de la extrusora en esto tiempo.

listing.name: Time Tracker - Chronos
listing.description:
Chronos is a Power-Up that brings work logs to Trello cards. It allows to track time, set estimate and get a report.

# Track time using Power-Up
For every card, Chronos provides an additional action button - "Start timer", which you can use to track time for the card.
![Track time using Power-Up](https://d19cgvjnjukyye.cloudfront.net/screenshots/track_time_using_powerup_v3.gif).
**Or you can add a work log manually**
![Add work log manually](https://d19cgvjnjukyye.cloudfront.net/screenshots/add_worklog_manually_v2.gif).

# Live tracking status update
Watch who is working on card live right on the board.
![Card badges](https://d19cgvjnjukyye.cloudfront.net/screenshots/card_badges_status.png).

# Reports
Fast and responsive report window for viewing work logs featuring many filtering and sorting options.
![Worklogs reports calendar](https://d19cgvjnjukyye.cloudfront.net/screenshots/worklogs_reports_calendar.png).
![Worklogs reports timeline](https://d19cgvjnjukyye.cloudfront.net/screenshots/worklogs_reports_timeline.png).

# Support and Feedback
We'd love to hear your feedback as you start using the Chronos. If you have any suggestions or run into any issues, please get in touch with us by contacting [Chronos Help Center](https://web-pal.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portals)
listing.overview: Seamless time tracking and reports. Track time right in a board. Track time without a hassle.
